Apple AirPods 3rd generation with Charging Case
The All-new Apple AirPods 3rd generation comes with Spatial Audio and dynamic head tracking that places sound all around you. It is equipped with Adaptive EQ that tunes the music to your ears. Inward-facing microphones detect what youâ€™re hearing, then adjust low- and mid-range frequencies to deliver the rich details in every song, customized for you in real-time. The force sensor gives you control over your entertainment. You can press to play, pause, skip through songs, or answer and end calls. It also has a longer battery life that charges up in a snap. You can Wirelessly and effortlessly recharge the MagSafe Charging Case on a MagSafe charger. The case gives you up to 30 hours of total listening time and charging AirPods in the case for just 5 minutes generates around an hour of listening time. It is equipped with an enhanced skin-detect sensor that knows the difference between your ear and other surfaces, so audio only plays when youâ€™re wearing AirPods and pauses when theyâ€™re in your pocket or on a table. You can track down your AirPods with the Find My app. See how close they are with proximity view, get separation alerts if theyâ€™re out of Bluetooth range. It has an IPX4 rating for Sweat & Water Resistance. Both AirPods and the MagSafe Charging Case are rated IPX4 sweat and water-resistant, so theyâ€™ll withstand anything from rain to heavy workouts. The Apple AirPods 3rd generation comes with no warranty.

Apple AirPods Pro 2nd Generation Wireless Earbuds with USB C Charging Case
The H2 chip enables a more tailored audio experience with Apple's 2nd generation AirPods Pro with Wireless MagSafe Charging Case, now with worldwide USB-C compatibility. The chip collaborates with a custom-built low-distortion driver, amplifier, and inward-facing mic in each ear to offer crisp highs, strong bass, and music that is tailored to your ear shape as you hear it. They also introduce a new dimension of sound with immersive Spatial Audio, which transports you to the stage alongside the band. Other improvements to the AirPods Pro include ANC with double the canceling strength, a transparency mode that adjusts to high-decibel noises, and more. But wait, there's more: when you pair your AirPods Pro with the separately available Apple Vision Pro, the H2 chip in these devices will communicate to transfer audio data at blisteringly fast speeds, delivering fully lossless audio with extremely low latency and elevating your mobile audio experience to incredible new heights. The Airpods Pro comes with four different sizes of silicone ear tip pairs as well as a USB-C charging cord.

Apple AirPods Max
The Apple AirPods Max have a stylish appearance and high-quality construction for excellent audio performance. It also has a fantastic active noise cancellation technology and a transparency mode that allow it to create high-quality audio noise-free. You can enjoy comfort when wearing and listening to music using AirPods. All things considered, it strikes the ideal balance between the seamless magic of AirPods and thrilling high-fidelity audio. The headphones provide the most comfortable and personalized listening experience.

It detects motion to make your movie clips sharp and exciting. The SJ4000 Air focuses on image quality and affordability. Although not waterproof out of the box, it comes with a 98' waterproof housing, which is also used to attach the camera to one of the several mounts included, such as the helmet mount. SJCAM SJ4000 Dual Screen Full HD WiFi Waterproof Sports Action Camera
The SJCAM SJ4000 Dual Screen Full HD WiFi Waterproof Sports Action Camera is a versatile and durable camera designed for adventure enthusiasts. With its 170° ultra-wide angle lens and 16MP camera, it allows you to capture stunning photos and videos in Full HD quality. Whether you're hiking, biking, surfing, or engaging in any other thrilling activity, this action camera is built to accompany you every step of the way. The SJCAM SJ4000 is a dual-screen design. It features a 2.0" high-definition main screen on the back and a 1.3" front screen, enabling you to easily frame your shots and preview your footage while you're on the move. This dual-screen setup is particularly beneficial for capturing self-portraits or group shots, as it allows you to see exactly what's being captured in real-time. Thanks to its WiFi compatibility, you can connect the camera to your smartphone or tablet and remotely control it from a distance of up to 10 meters. This feature comes in handy when you want to position the camera in hard-to-reach places or capture shots from unique angles. You can also conveniently transfer your photos and videos wirelessly to your mobile device for instant sharing with friends and family. The SJCAM SJ4000 is built to withstand the elements. It comes with durable waterproof housing that enables you to take the camera underwater to depths of up to 30 meters. Whether you're snorkeling, diving, or simply enjoying a day at the beach, this camera allows you to capture the mesmerizing underwater world with ease. The SJCAM SJ4000 Dual Screen Full HD WiFi Waterproof Sports Action Camera is a reliable and feature-packed device for capturing your adventures. AMD Ryzen 5 5500 Processor is 6 processor cores, 12 threads, and an astonishingly efficient 45-65W TDP. This processor, It stands with 3.9GHz Base Clock, 4.4GHz Max Boost Clock, 3MB L2 Cache, 16MB L3 Cache with AM4 Package, and TSMC 7nm FinFET CMOS. This processor is built with PCIe 3.0 x8 and Wraith Spire Thermal Solution. The AMD Ryzen 5 5500 Processor provides DDR4 Up to 3200MHz memory with 2 memory channels. It has AMD StoreMI Technology. A fast and easy way to expand and accelerate the storage in a desktop PC with an AMD Ryzen processor. AMD StoreMI technology is a powerful tool for PC enthusiasts that want to improve load times, boot times, file management, or system responsiveness. Whatever your storage acceleration needs, AMD StoreMI technology automatically pairs your most-used files with an SSD cache for peak performance.  MD StoreMI technology can get files running at SSD-like speeds. Simply add an SSD to your system and let StoreMI do the rest. It also has AMD "Zen 3" Core Architecture with the fastest cores in the world for PC gamers. The "Zen 3" architecture represents the most comprehensive design overhaul of the "Zen" era. Over 20 major changes include wider and more flexible execution resources; significantly more load/store bandwidth to feed execution; and a streamlined front-end to get more threads in flight and do it faster. The "Zen 3" architecture can extract an average of 19% additional performance from every MHz of frequency relative to the previous generation2. This is a historically large generational improvement in IPC, and a major player in the architectureâ€™s ability to deliver unmatched single-core performance. The "Zen 3" architecture transitions to a new "unified complex" design that brings 8 cores and 32MB of L3 cache into a single group of resources. This dramatically reduces core-to-core and core-to-cache latencies by making every element of the die a next-door neighbor with minimal communication time. Latency-sensitive tasks like PC gaming especially benefit from this change, as tasks now have direct access to twice as much L3 cache versus the Zen 2. It also features the AMD Ryzen VR-Ready Premium for the best possible VR experiences, AMD offers select Ryzenâ„¢ VR-Ready Premium processors. AMD Ryzen 5 5500 Processor offers a 3-years warranty(No Warranty for Fan or Cooler).

The AMD Ryzen 5 8600G 4.3 GHz Six-Core AM5 Processor raises the bar for gaming and content production with six cores, 12 threads, and a dedicated AI engine. Furthermore, the AMD Ryzen AI engine utilizes the processor's specialized NPU, GPU, and processing cores to boost AI tasks with compatible apps. This unlocked CPU may be overclocked to increase performance even more.
